%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sanjay%20Singh%20Is%203rd%20AAP%20Leader%20To%20Be%20Arrested%20By%20A%20Central%20Agency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faaps-sanjay-singh-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-money-laundering-case-4449484%5C%22%3E%20Sanjay%20Singh%20was%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20today%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy-linked%20money%20laundering%20case.%20He%20is%20the%20third%20AAP%20leader%20to%20be%20arrested%20by%20a%20central%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20him%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested%20earlier%20this%20year%20and%20Satyendar%20Jain%20was%20arrested%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20also%20questioned%20for%20nearly%20nine%20hours%20by%20the%20CBI%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20He%20was%20questioned%20as%20a%20witness%20in%20the%20case%20which%20investogators%20said%20involved%20corruption%20in%20framing%20the%20policy%20to%20benefit%20a%20liquor%20lobby.%20He%20hasn't%20been%20summoned%20for%20further%20questioning%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20raided%20Mr%20Singh's%20home.%20The%20ED%20had%20earlier%20questioned%20members%20of%20the%20staff%20and%20those%20linked%20to%20the%2051-year-old%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EComing%20out%20in%20support%20of%20his%20party%20MP%2C%C2%A0%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20that%20nothing%20will%20be%20found%20at%20his%20residence%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20agencies%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-aap-mp-sanjay-singh-arrested-by-probe-agency-in-liquor-policy-case-live-updates-sanjay-singh-arrest-live-4449528%5C%22%3EEnforcement%20Directorate%20or%20ED%20and%20CBI%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewill%20get%20active%20as%20the%202024%20elections%20are%20coming.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EManish%20Sisodia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20on%20February%2026%20arrested%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20then%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%2C%20for%20alleged%20corruption%20in%20the%20formulation%20and%20implementation%20of%20the%20now-scrapped%20Delhi%20Excise%20Policy%202021-22.%20He%20has%20been%20in%20custody%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20on%20February%2028%2C%20he%20resigned%20from%20the%20Delhi%20cabinet%20on%20February%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Sisodia%20held%20the%20excise%20portfolio%20among%20the%20many%20that%20he%20handled%20as%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20arrested%20him%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20stemming%20from%20the%20CBI%20FIR%20on%20March%209%20after%20questioning%20him%20in%20Tihar%20Jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20federal%20investigative%20agencies%2C%20irregularities%20were%20committed%20while%20modifying%20the%20excise%20policy%20and%20undue%20favours%20were%20extended%20to%20licence%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20implemented%20the%20policy%20on%20November%2017%2C%202021%2C%20but%20scrapped%20it%20at%20the%20end%20of%20September%202022%20amid%20allegations%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESatyendar%20Jain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20Delhi%20minister%20Satyendar%20Jain%20was%20arrested%20in%20May%20last%20year%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20arrested%20the%20AAP%20leader%20on%20the%20charge%20of%20laundering%20money%20through%20four%20companies%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20is%20based%20on%20a%20CBI%20complaint%20registered%20on%20the%20allegation%20that%20Satyendar%20Jain%20had%20acquired%20movable%20properties%20in%20the%20name%20of%20various%20persons%20from%20February%2014%2C%202015%2C%20to%20May%2031%2C%202017%2C%20which%20he%20could%20not%20satisfactorily%20account