ian-games-2023-live-updates-neeraj-chopra-javelin-throw-final-latest-score-4448954%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fasian-games-2023-live-updates-neeraj-chopra-javelin-throw-final-latest-score-4448954%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fasian-games-2023-live-updates-neeraj-chopra-javelin-throw-final-latest-score-4448954%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AAP's%20Sanjay%20Singh%20Arrested%20In%20Delhi%20Liquor%20Policy%20Case%20Hours%20After%20Raids%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20yet%20another%20blow%20for%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20arrested%20its%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy.%20Searches%20were%20being%20conducted%20at%20the%20Delhi%20residence%20of%20the%20MP%20since%20early%20on%20Wednesday%20morning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20third%20major%20arrest%20from%20the%20party.%20Delhi%20Health%20Minister%20Satyendar%20Jain%20was%20arrested%20in%20May%20last%20year%20on%20charges%20of%20laundering%20money%20through%20four%20companies%20that%20were%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20setback%20for%20the%20party%2C%20however%2C%20came%20in%20February%20this%20year%2C%20when%20then%20Delhi%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20close%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20aide%20Manish%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20in%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20raids%20against%20Mr%20Singh%20took%20place%20after%20he%20was%20named%20by%20businessman%20Dinesh%20Arora%2C%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20who%20later%20turned%20'approver'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Arora%20claimed%20that%20the%20AAP%20leader%20had%20introduced%20him%20to%20Mr%20Sisodia%2C%20who%20was%20the%20excise%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaids%2C%20Defence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESearch%20operations%20began%20at%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP's%20residence%20early%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20and%20went%20on%20for%20a%20few%20hours.%20AAP%20workers%20reached%20his%20house%20and%20raised%20slogans%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bmisuse%26quot%3B%20of%20agencies.%20Additional%20police%20personnel%20were%20posted%20to%20prevent%20the%20situation%20from%20escalating.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20office%2C%20where%20his%20statement%20will%20be%20recorded.%20He%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20produced%20in%20court%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon%20and%20the%20agency%20is%20expected%20to%20seek%20his%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20came%20out%20in%20support%20of%20his%20colleague%20while%20the%20raids%20were%20being%20conducted%20and%2C%20without%20naming%20the%20BJP%2C%20accused%20the%20party%20of%20engaging%20in%20desperate%20attempts%20to%20derail%20rivals%20ahead%20of%20next%20year's%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20last%20year%20we%20have%20been%20hearing%20noise%20about%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20scam.%20More%20than%201%2C000%20raids%20have%20been%20conducted%20and%20not%20a%20single%20paisa%20was%20recovered.%20They%20just%20keep%20alleging%20'scam'...%20I%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20investigation%20and%20found%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20is%20going%20to%20be%20found%20from%20Sanjay%20Singh's%20place%20too.%20Elections%20are%20coming%20and%20they%20feel%20(they)%20are%20losing...%20so%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20last%20desperate%20attempt%20of%20the%20losing%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20news%20of%20the%20arrest%20came%20out%2C%20Mr%20Raghav%20Chadha%20made%20similar%20allegations%20and%20did%20not%20shy%20away%20from%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20been%20investigating%20the%20case%20for%2015%20months%20but%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20unearth%20even%20a%20single%20rupee%20of%20illegal%20money.%20So%20much%20time%20and%20so%20many%20resources%20have%20been%20expended%20but%20they%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20prove%20anything.%20This%20is%20just%20a%20political%20vendetta.%20The%20BJP%20knows%20it%20is%20losing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696423380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-09%2Fvd9grjfc_aap-leader-sanjay-singh-pti_625x300_19_September_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faaps-sanjay-singh-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-money-laundering-case-4449484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20yet%20another%20blow%20for%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20arrested%20its%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faaps-sanjay-singh-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-money-laundering-case-4449484%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faaps-sanjay-singh-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-money-laundering-case-4449484%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faaps-sanjay-singh-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-money-laundering-case-4449484%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22National%20Rights%20Body%20Condemns%20Action%20Against%20Newsclick%2C%20Highlights%20Disabled%20Status%20of%20Detainee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F10154711%2FUntitled-design-2021-02-10T154651.122.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20National%20Platform%20for%20the%20Rights%20of%20the%20Disabled%20(NPRD)%20has%20released%20a%20statement%20strongly%20condemning%20the%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20attack%20on%20the%20independent%20media%20outlet%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ehighlighting%20the%20fact%20that%20one%20of%20those%20arrested%20is%20a%C2%A0polio%20survivor%20and%20person%20with%20disability%2C%20who%20uses%20crutches.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20two%20detained%20%E2%80%93%20after%2046%20persons%20linked%20to%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20subjected%20to%20raids%2C%20device%20seizures%20and%20questionings%20on%20October%203%20%E2%80%93%20and%20remanded%20to%20police%20custody%20is%20Amit%20Chakravarti.%20The%20statement%20notes%20that%20as%20a%20person%20with%20disability%2C%20he%20has%20a%20right%20to%20be%20protected%20from%20inhuman%20treatment%20and%20torture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChakravarthi%20is%20an%20administrator%20at%20Newsclick%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fdelhi-police-conducts-early-morning-raids-at-houses-of-journalists-satirists%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%2C%20signed%20by%20general%20secretary%20Muralidharan%2C%20also%20says%20that%20the%20portal%20has%20been%C2%A0consistently%20championing%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20marginalised%20sections%2C%20including%20disabled%20people.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20people-centric%20approach%2C%20the%20portal%20has%20been%20consistently%20carrying%20reports%20and%20articles%20on%20various%20struggles%20and%20issues%20of%20the%20disabled%20community%20and%20sought%20to%20lend%20a%20voice%20to%20their%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20reminds%20of%20the%20UN%20conventions%20on%20the%20rights%20of%20persons%20with%20disabilities%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArticle%2025%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Convention%20on%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(UNCRPD)%20affirms%20that%20the%20State%20shall%20%E2%80%9CPrevent%20discriminatory%20denial%20of%20health%20care%20or%20health%20services%20or%20food%20and%20fluids%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20disability.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%2C%202016%20under%20Section%206%20provides%20for%20%E2%80%9CProtection%20from%20cruelty%20and%20inhuman%20treatment%E2%80%9D.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20legislation%20and%20convention%20on%20disability%20the%20right%20to%20protection%20from%20torture%2C%20cruel%2C%20inhuman%20and%20degrading%20treatment%20and%20the%20right%20to%20be%20treated%20with%20humanity%20and%20respect%20for%20inherent%20dignity%20for%20those%20lawfully%20deprived%20of%20their%20liberty%20is%20specified%20under%20Articles%207%20%26amp%3B%2010%20of%20International%20Covenant%20on%20Civil%20and%20Political%20Rights%20(ICCPR).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NPRD%20has%20asked%20that%20all%20reasonable%20accommodations%20should%20be%20provided%20to%20Amit%20Chakravarti%20while%20he%20is%20in%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUntil%20his%20release%20he%20should%20be%20lodged%20in%20a%20facilities%20that%20takes%20care%20of%20his%20accessibility%20needs.%20His%20other%20needs%20as%20a%20disabled%20person%20should%20be%20complied%20with%2C%20including%20but%20not%20restricted%20to%20health%20concerns%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696423246000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F10154711%2FUntitled-design-2021-02-10T154651.122.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnational-platform-for-the-rights-of-the-disabled-newsclick-amit-chakravarti%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20statement%20National%20Platform%20for%20the%20Rights%20of%20the%20Disabled%20also%20says%20that%20the%20portal%20has%20been%C2%A0consistently%20championing%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20marginalised%20sections%2C%20including