una%20rivers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20warned%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20to%20comply%20with%20its%20orders%20on%20pain%20of%20further%20action.%20A%20bench%20led%20by%20Justice%20SK%20Kaul%20told%20the%20Punjab%20government%20it%20%26quot%3Bhas%20to%20accept%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emaryada%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(decorum)%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20told%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann's%20administration%20%26quot%3B...%20don't%20compel%20us%20to%20issue%20tough%20orders%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20directed%20the%20centre%20to%20oversee%20talks%20between%20Punjab%20and%20the%20Haryana%20governments%20on%20this%20topic%3B%20the%20latter%20has%20completed%20construction%20of%20its%20half%20of%20the%20canal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20that%20also%20included%20Justice%20CT%20Ravikumar%20and%20Justice%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20also%20told%20the%20centre%20to%20take%20over%20and%20complete%20pre-construction%20land%20surveys%20and%20re-listed%20the%20matter%20for%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20concerned%20with%20(non-)execution%20of%20a%20decree%20for%20construction%20of%20a%20canal%20(in%20the)%20Punjab%20portion.%20We%20would%20like%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20to%20survey%20the%20portion%20of%20land%20allocated...%20An%20estimate%20has%20to%20be%20made%20for%20extent%20of%20construction%20(needed)...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20legal%20news%20website%20Live%20Law%2C%20at%20today's%20hearing%2C%20counsel%20for%20the%20Punjab%20government%20blamed%20the%20delay%20on%20pressure%20from%20the%20opposition%20and%20problems%20acquiring%20land%20from%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20may%20be%20political%20implications%20(but)%20something%20has%20to%20be%20done.%20Canal%20will%20have%20to%20be%20constructed%20in%20Punjab...%20do%20not%20compel%20us%20to%20issue%20tough%20orders%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20irate%20top%20court%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Haryana%20side%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20only%20thing%20that%20remains%20is%20construction.%20Punjab%2C%20of%20course%2C%20has%20to%20co-operate.%20That%20is%20what%20federalism%20is%20about...%20we%20have%20to%20move%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20(the%20two%20states)%20solve%20matter%20together...%20do%20not%20force%20us%20to%20issue%20strict%20orders%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20get%20into%20it...%20you%20will%20have%20to%20find%20a%20solution.%26quot%3B%20The%20court%20then%20turned%20to%20the%20centre's%20representative%20and%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20Union%20of%20India%2C%20what%20are%20you%20doing%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday's%20hearing%20comes%20a%20week%20after%20Mr%20Mann%20met%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20Amritsar%20and%20strongly%20opposed%20construction%20of%20the%20canal%20from%20his%20side.%20He%20called%20the%20canal%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20emotive%20issue%26quot%3B%20for%20Punjab%20and%20said%20building%20it%20may%20lead%20to%20law-and-order%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgive-chandigarh-to-punjab-no-spare-water-to-share-says-punjab-cm-mann-at-nzc-meeting-4426603%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGive%20Chandigarh%20To%20Punjab%2C%20No%20Spare%20Water%20To%20Share%3A%20Bhagwant%20Mann%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3ECongress%2C%20AAP%2C%20BJP%20Respond%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20rare%20show%20of%20unity%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20have%20both%20backed%20the%20AAP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Amarinder%20Raja%20Warring%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20respect%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20but%20Punjab%20has%20no%20water%20to%20give%20to%20anyone.%20We%20cannot%20give%20water%20by%20killing%20rights%20of%20our%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20l