%3BThough%20AAP%20spokesperson%20and%20party%20maintain%20Punjab%20can't%20share%20river%20water%2C%20it's%20counsel%20in%20Supreme%20Court%20blames%20opposition%20pressure%20for%20not%20building%20canal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Court%20Said%20Earlier%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20hearing%20in%20this%20case%20-%20in%20July%20four%20years%20ago%20-%20the%20court%20ordered%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20chief%20ministers%20(then%20Amarinder%20Singh%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20respectively)%20to%20meet%20and%20find%20an%20amicable%20solution%20to%20the%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3ESutlej-Yamuna%20Link%20Canal%20Row%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20stems%20from%20a%20controversial%201981%20water-sharing%20agreement%20drawn%20up%20Haryana%20was%20carved%20out%20of%20Punjab%20in%201966.%20For%20effective%20allocation%2C%20the%20canal%20was%20to%20be%20constructed%20and%20the%20two%20states%20were%20required%20to%20construct%20respective%20portions%20within%20their%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20the%20then%20Punjab%20government%20passed%20a%20law%20scrapping%20the%20SYL%20deal%20and%20similar%20pacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20hit%20back%20in%202016%2C%20striking%20down%20the%20law.%20Punjab%2C%20however%2C%20went%20ahead%20and%20returned%20the%20land%20on%20which%20the%20canal%20was%20to%20be%20constructed%20to%20the%20landowners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696422240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-03%2Fsutlej-yamuna-link-canal_650x400_51458309667.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsutlej-yam