.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParticipation%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-jobs-gig-work-engagement-productivity-gallup-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egig%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20tends%20to%20attract%20younger%20and%20lower-income%20people%2C%20though%20more%20than%20half%20of%20each%20generation%20and%20income%20bracket%20participated%20at%20some%20point%20in%20the%20gig%20economy%20as%20a%20source%20of%20income.%20This%20value%20is%2068%25%20for%20millennials%20and%2067%25%20for%20Gen%20Z%2C%20which%20suggests%20that%20younger%20generations%20are%20attracted%20to%20these%20roles%20due%20to%20greater%20flexibility%2C%20mobility%2C%20and%20self-determination.%20This%20compares%20to%2058%25%20of%20Gen%20X%20and%2052%25%20of%20baby%20boomers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgig-economy-trends-workers-delivery-ride-hailing-apps-uber-doordash-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egig%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20or%20contract%20work%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0continues%20to%20rise%2C%20many%20younger%20workers%20are%20flocking%20to%20these%20positions%2C%20citing%20opportunities%20to%20make%20more%20money%2C%20work%20a%20more%20convenient%20schedule%2C%20or%20try%20a%20new%20career%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20strong%20job%20market%2C%20using%20gig%20platforms%20as%20a%20primary%20income%20source%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20decision%20made%20amid%20an%20abundance%20of%20options%20rather%20than%20desperation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20most%20sought-after%20freelance%20positions%20for%20all%20generations%20are%20contractors%20for%20in-person%20tasks%2C%20digital%20freelancers%2C%20grocery%20delivery%2C%20food%20delivery%2C%20and%20ride%20share%20drivers.%20Around%2040%25%20of%20ride%20share%20drivers%20reported%20making%20%245%2C000%20or%20more%20a%20month%2C%20compared%20to%20around%2035%25%20for%20grocery%20delivery%20and%2031%25%20for%20digital%20freelancers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20likely%20these%20numbers%20will%20grow%20in%20the%20future%2C%20as%20for%20instance%2C%2038%25%20of%20people%20say%20they%20will%20participate%20in%20grocery%20delivery%20in%20the%20future%20despite%20only%2022%25%20currently%20working%20in%20that%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbfi.uchicago.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2FBFI_WP_2023-69.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eworking%20paper%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20May%202023%20found%20that%20the%20number%20of%20platform%20gig%20workers%20increased%20from%201.8%20million%20in%202019%20to%204.9%20million%20in%202021%2C%20corresponding%20to%20a%20170%25%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20opportunities%20for%20them%20to%20make%20money%20in%20this%20space%20and%20for%20them%20to%20either%20supplement%20or%20have%20that%20be%20their%20high%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20Lazos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20report%20notes%20how%20gig%20platforms%20are%20at%20risk%20due%20to%20falling%20inflation%2C%20a%20still-hot%20job%20market%2C%20and%20lingering%20economic%20uncertainty.%20Common%20reasons%20people%20stopped%20doing%20gig%20work%20included%20getting%20a%20full-time%20job%20or%20a%20raise%2C%20not%20making%20enough%20money%20or%20working%20too%20few%20hours%2C%20and%20safety%20concerns.%20Nearly%20one%20in%20four%20gig%20workers%20have%20been%20victimized%20by%20fraud%20or%20identity%20theft%20while%20using%20gig%20platforms%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20double%20the%20rate%20of%20those%20not%20using%20gig%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20recently%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-us-unemployment-rate-labor-market-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJob%20Openings%20and%20Labor%20Turnover%20Survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealed%20there%20are%20still%20almost%209%20million%20job%20openings%20nationwide%20%E2%80%94%20even%20with%20unemployment%20at%20historic%20lows%20%E2%80%94%20which%20suggests%20many%20companies%20are%20looking%20to%20fill%20those%20spots%20by%20competing%20with%20gig%20platforms.%20Given%20real%20income%20is%20growing%2C%20some%20gig%20platforms%20are%20struggling%20to%20attract%20new%20workers%20while%20keeping%20services%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20recently%20taken%20up%20gig%20work%20as%20your%20primary%20income%20source%3F%20Have%20you%20made%20the%20switch%20from%20a%20full-time%20job%20to%20a%20gig%20job%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ensheidlower%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgig-workers-millennials-and-gen-z-out-earn-older-workers-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696420921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651b2d0c617692f0d03d05ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgig-workers-millennials-and-gen-z-out-earn-older-workers-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20millennials%20are%20switching%20to%20gig%20roles%20like%20contractors%20and%20delivery%20drivers%20as%20their%20primary%20source%20of%20income.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nsheidlower%40insider.com%20(Noah%20Sheidlower)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgig-workers-millennials-and-gen-z-out-earn-older-workers-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ayodhya%3A%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%20Stirs%20Controversy%20Again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F19110544%2Ffull-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAyodhya%E2%80%99s%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%20finds%20itself%20in%20a%20fresh%20controversy%20after%20it%20was%20accused%20by%20the%20Naga%20sadhus%20of%20the%20Hanuman%20Garhi%20temple%20of%20attempting%20to%20fraudulently%20grab%20land%20at%20Angad%20Tila.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Trust%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fram-temple-trust-statement-on-allegations-of-scam-in-ayodhya-deal-7360119%2F%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20corruption%20in%20land%20deals.%20Similar%20allegations%20have%20once%20again%20surfaced%20now%20and%20this%20time%2C%20it%20is%20not%20any%20political%20party%20or%20leader%20but%20Hanuman%20Garhi%20locals%20who%20have%20levelled%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Naga%20sadhus%20of%20the%20Hanuman%20Garhi%20temple%20have%20opened%20a%20front%20against%20the%20Trust%20for%20allegedly%20attempting%20to%20fraudulently%20grab%20land%20at%20Angad%20Tila%20(a%20small%20hillock)%20claimed%20by%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EGarhi%2C%20and%20have%20also%20threatened%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20major%20agitation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sadhus%20allege%20that%20after%20the%20Trust%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20occupy%20the%20said%20land%20by%20pressuring%20the%20Garhi%20failed%2C%20it%20used%20its%20influence%20on%20the%20local%20administration%20to%20get%20this%20land%20declared%20as%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enazul%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20land%E2%80%99%20(non-agricultural%20government%20land).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20claim%20that%20the%20land%20in%20question%20has%20been%20in%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%20Garhi%20since%20the%2013th%20century%2C%20for%20which%20documentary%20proof%20is%20also%20available.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20clarification%20issued%20in%20response%20to%20the%20allegation%2C%20the%20Trust%20said%20that%20the%20action%20of%20the%20administration%20is%20beyond%20its%20control%20and%20hence%20it%20cannot%20be%20held%20responsible%20for%20the%20decision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20Garhi%E2%80%99s%20sadhus%20insist%20that%20the%20only%20purpose%20behind%20declaring%20the%20said%20land%20as%20nazul%20is%20to%20facilitate%20its%20transfer%20to%20the%20Trust%20and%20allege%20collusion%20between%20the%20administration%20and%20the%20Trust.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20June%202021%2C%20the%20Trust%20was%20accused%20of%20corruption%20in%20land%20deals%20by%20opposition%20parties%2C%20and%20amid%20vociferous%20demands%20for%20an%20investigation%2C%20it%20could%20not%20even%20muster%20a%20clarification.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20allegations%2C%20the%20Trust%20had%20extensively%20used%20its%20influence%20in%20the%20incumbent%20government%20and%20administration%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20alleged%20corruption.%20The%20names%20of%20a%20BJP%20MLA%2C%20the%20Ayodhya%20mayor%E2%80%99s%20nephew%20and%20a%20government%20official%20also%20surfaced%20in%20this%20connection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20one%20of%20his%20reports%2C%20a%20local%20journalist%20quoted%20a%20property%20dealer%20as%20saying%20that%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20(then)%20district%20magistrate%20Anuj%20Kumar%20Jha%20had%20visited%20him%20three%20or%20four%20times%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20land%20deal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-august-5-bhoomi-pujan%5C%22%3EThe%20Political%20Undertones%20of%20Choosing%20August%205%20for%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple%20%E2%80%98Bhoomi%20Pujan%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20Trust%20did%20not%20bother%20to%20learn%20any%20lesson%20from%20the%20entire%20episode.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20when%20preparations%20are%20being%20made%20for%20the%20installation%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20%E2%80%93%20the%20statue%20of%20a%20child%20Ram%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20newly%20built%20Ram%20temple%20amid%20much%20fanfare%2C%20the%20Trust%20has%20been%20forced%20to%20issue%20a%20clarification%20after%20getting%20embroiled%20in%20this%20dispute%20over%20%E2%80%98grabbing%E2%80%99%201.6%20acres%20of%20land%20at%20Angad%20Tila%20adjacent%20to%20the%20temple%20premises.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Naga%20sadhus%2C%20the%20Trust%20is%20trying%20to%20annex%20the%20land%20at%20Angad%20Tila%20by%20hook%20or%20by%20crook%20as%20part%20of%20its%20plan%20to%20expand%20the%20Ram%20temple%20complex.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECurrently%2C%20a%20portion%20of%20Angad%20Tila%20is%20inside%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20complex%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%20part%20is%20outside%20its%20barricading.%20The%20Naga%20sadhus%20claim%20that%20the%20Hardwari%20belt%20of%20the%20Garhi%20has%20been%20cultivating%20flowers%20on%20this%20land%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20Trust%20has%20been%20pressuring%20the%20claimants%20of%20the%20Garhi%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20said%20piece%20of%20land%20and%20has%20also%20been%20getting%20some%20construction%20done%20facing%20towards%20the%20Garhi.%20The%20Trust%20also%20tried%20to%20install%20a%20gate%20in%20the%20double%20barricading%20of%20the%20temple%20complex%20in%20their%20direction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20instead%20of%20talks%20resolving%20anything%2C%20the%20matter%20got%20complicated%2C%20and%20when%20the%20Garhi%20expressed%20its%20intention%20to%20build%20a%20shelter%20for%2045%20sadhus%20who%20were%20made%20homeless%20after%20many%20shelters%20of%20sadhus%20on%20the%20said%20land%20came%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20Ram%2C%20Bhakti%20and%20Janmabhoomi%20Paths%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20the%20local%20administration%20had%20declared%20the%20said%20land%20as%20nazul%20land%20in%20government%20documents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAngered%20by%20this%2C%20the%20Naga%20sadhus%20reached%20the%20said%20land%20and%20not%20only%20started%20religious%20rituals%2C%20prayers%20and%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elangar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20also%20demolished%20whatever%20structures%20the%20Trust%20had%20erected%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Naga%20sadhus%20have%20been%20camping%20at%20the%20site%20since%20September%2023.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20Trust%20at%20Angad%20Tila%20have%20come%20to%20a%20standstill%2C%20while%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20pacify%20the%20Naga%20sadhus%20through%20a%20magistrate%20remained%20inconclusive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMahant%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Sanjay%20Das%2C%20the%20national%20president%20of%20the%20Sankatmochan%20Sena%2C%20which%20is%20affiliated%20with%20the%20Hanuman%20Garhi%20temple%2C%20rejected%20the%20Trust%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20after%20a%20deadlock%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20Garhi%20regarding%20the%20land%20at%20Angad%20Tila%2C%20it%20had%20distanced%20itself%20from%20the%20matter%20and%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20said%20land%20being%20declared%20as%20nazul.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDas%20alleged%20that%20it%20was%20quite%20clear%20who%20prompted%20the%20administration%20to%20suddenly%20declare%20the%20said%20land%20as%20nazul.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EQuestion%20on%20benches%20installed%20on%20Janmabhoomi%20Path%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20building%20construction%20committee%20of%20the%20Trust%2C%20Nripendra%20Mishra%2C%20recently%20alleged%20that%20the%20benches%20installed%20by%20the%20public%20works%20department%20(PWD)%20for%20the%20convenience%20of%20pilgrims%20on%20the%20Janmabhoomi%20Path%20from%20Birla%20Dharamshala%20in%20Ayodhya%20to%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20are%20substandard.%20However%2C%20the%20controversy%20was%20short-lived.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20600-metre%20stretch%20is%20being%20constructed%20by%20the%20PWD.%20Questions%20have%20been%20raised%20regarding%20its%20quality%20and%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20in%20many%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20details%20received%20during%20one%20of%20his%20inspections%2C%20Mishra%20found%20the%20pink%20sandstone%20benches%20installed%20along%20the%20Janmabhoomi%20Path%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98slimmer%E2%80%99%20than%20expected%2C%20so%20he%20summoned%20the%20concerned%20architect%20and%20asked%20him%20about%20the%20thickness%20of%20the%20stones%20approved%20for%20the%20benches%20to%20be%20installed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20he%20was%20told%20that%20it%20was%20six%20to%20four-and-a-half%20inches%2C%20Mishra%20further%20asked%20why%20thinner%20stones%20with%20a%20thickness%20of%20less%20than%20three%20inches%20were%20installed%20on%20the%20benches%E2%80%99%20seats%2C%20and%20whether%20any%20decision%20had%20been%20taken%20regarding%20changes%20in%20thickness%20or%20design%20and%20at%20what%20stage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20architect%E2%80%99s%20reply%20failed%20to%20satisfy%20him%2C%20he%20summoned%20the%20entire%20file%20from%20the%20chief%20engineer%20of%20the%20PWD%2C%20Dharamveer%20Singh%2C%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20ensure%20accountability.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMishra%20also%20sought%20information%20as%20to%20how%20many%20such%20benches%20have%20been%20installed%20in%20total.%20He%20was%20informed%20that%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20total%20of%2070%20benches%20was%20proposed%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20half%20of%20which%20had%20been%20installed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20reports%20of%20corruption%20in%20the%20installation%20of%20benches%20soon%20spread%20and%20caused%20a%20stir%2C%20but%20later%2C%20Singh%20ended%20all%20speculation%20by%20claiming%20that%20Mishra%20had%20been%20handed%20a%20complete%20test%20report%20along%20with%20the%20approved%20design%20of%20the%20benches%20as%20per%20his%20demand%20and%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%98satisfied%E2%80%99%20with%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20building%20construction%20committee%20headed%20by%20Mishra%20also%20endorsed%20his%20approval.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fas-ram-mandir-nears-completion-ayodhyas-traders-bear-hidden-costs%5C%22%3EAs%20Ram%20Mandir%20Nears%20Completion%2C%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20Traders%20Bear%20Hidden%20Costs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20about%20local%20journalists%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Ayodhya%2C%20preparations%20for%20the%20proposed%20consecration%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20January%202024%20are%20in%20full%20swing.%20Amidst%20all%20fanfare%2C%20many%20journalists%20recently%20quoted%20Champat%20Rai%2C%20the%20Trust%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%2C%20as%20saying%20that%20during%20the%20installation%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esants%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20mahants%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20enter%20the%20Ram%20temple%20premises%20with%20religious%20items%20such%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20chhatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20chanwar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20paduka%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20Champat%20Rai%20said%20that%20this%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20tight%20security%20of%20VVIPs%20arriving%20at%20the%20function.%20He%20added%20that%20in%20order%20to%20follow%20safety%20standards%2C%20guests%20may%20have%20to%20walk%20one%20or%20two%20kilometres.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20view%20of%20this%2C%20he%20also%20appealed%20to%20elderly%20people%20who%20have%20lost%20the%20ability%20to%20walk%20or%20sit%20up%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20as%20due%20to%20tight%20security%20arrangements%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20sit%20at%20the%20venue%20for%20three%20to%20four%20hours.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20only%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20leaves%20will%20the%20people%20sitting%20inside%20be%20able%20to%20catch%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20expected%20that%20sadhus%20and%20sants%20would%20be%20the%20first%20to%20react%20to%20the%20news%2C%20formally%20or%20informally%2C%20because%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echhatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echanwar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epaduka%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20a%20part%20of%20their%20identity.%20But%20the%20reaction%20came%20from%20local%20journalists%20instead.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20controversy%20erupted%20when%20a%20senior%20journalist%20referred%20to%20the%20above%20news%20in%20the%20WhatsApp%20group%20of%20the%20local%20press%20club%20and%20asked%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20what%20about%20the%20local%20journalists%3F%20What%20if%20they%20try%20to%20enter%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20journalist%20intended%20to%20ask%20about%20the%20conditions%20for%20local%20journalists%20to%20gain%20entry%20and%20whether%20or%20not%20they%20would%20be%20allowed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20backdrop%20for%20the%20question%20was%20the%20recent%20refusal%20to%20permit%20local%20journalists%20to%20attend%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20programme%20in%20Ayodhya%20recently.%20The%20officials%20of%20the%20Press%20Club%20were%20expected%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20question%20or%20at%20least%20ask%20the%20journalist%20to%20take%20up%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20matter%20remained%20limited%20to%20the%20reaction%20of%20a%20journalist%20associated%20with%20an%20English%20newspaper%20who%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSome%20journalists%20are%20dear%20to%20Babu%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eji%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20These%20journalists%20bow%20down%20to%20Babuji.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20journalist%20who%20raised%20the%20question%2C%20many%20journalists%20who%20spoke%20to%20him%20considered%20his%20question%20relevant%20but%20refused%20to%20take%20any%20public%20stand%20on%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20according%20to%20experts%2C%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20depend%20on%20local%20journalists%20for%20its%20campaign%20in%20Ayodhya%20anymore%2C%20as%20the%20topmost%20media%20houses%20manage%20its%20programs%20and%20events%20and%20local%20journalists%20have%20no%20role%20in%20it.%20Therefore%2C%20neither%20the%20party%20nor%20the%20administration%20pays%20them%20much%20heed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fkrishna-pratap-singh%5C%22%3EThe%20writer%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F258624%2Fayodhya-ram-janmbhoomi-teerth-trust-land-dispute-ayodhya-seers%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20Hindi%20original%