money%20through%20the%20Mahadev%20Gaming%20app.%20ED%20has%20said%20that%20it%20is%20an%20umbrella%20syndicate%20that%20promotes%20betting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Mahadev%20Gaming%20app%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20provides%20platforms%20for%20illegal%20betting%20in%20different%20live%20games%20like%20Poker%2C%20card%20games%2C%20chance%20games%2C%20badminton%2C%20tennis%2C%20football%20as%20well%20as%20betting%20on%20cricket%2C%20along%20with%20the%20provision%20for%20playing%20a%20number%20of%20card%20games%20like%20Teen%20Patti%20(a%20card%20game)%2C%20Poker%2C%20Dragon%20Tiger%2C%20and%20virtual%20cricket%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20who%20maintain%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franbir-kapoor-summoned-by-enforcement-directorate-over-case-involving-gaming-app-4449006%5C%22%3EMahadev%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20operate%20a%20number%20of%20closed%20groups%20on%20various%20instant%20messaging%20platforms.%20They%20also%20run%204-5%20similar%20platforms%20and%20reportedly%20make%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%20200%20crore%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20modus%20operandi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20advertise%20contact%20number%20over%20websites%20and%20lure%20people%20to%20play%20to%20earn%20profits.%20Such%20numbers%20can%20only%20be%20contacted%20on%20platforms%20like%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20user%20contacts%20the%20given%20number%2C%20he%2Fshe%20will%20be%20provided%20two%20separate%20contact%20numbers.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20for%20depositing%20money%20and%20collecting%20points%20in%20user%20IDs%20used%20to%20make%20bets%2C%20while%20the%20second%20number%20is%20for%20contacting%20the%20website%20to%20encash%20the%20accumulated%20points%20in%20the%20designated%20IDs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IDs%20are%20generally%20created%20on%20multiple%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20games%20are%20rigged%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20overall%20the%2