n-fans-fighting-over-malavika-mohanan%2Farticleshow%2F104159673.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranbir%20Kapoor%20Summoned%20By%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20In%20Gaming%20App%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20on%20Friday%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20case%20involving%20a%20gaming%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20has%20featured%20in%20several%20commercials%20promoting%20the%20app.%20The%20probe%20agency%20has%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20given%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20money%20in%20exchange%2C%20which%20was%20from%20the%20proceeds%20of%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMahadev%20Online%20Book%20App%2C%20the%20app%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20controversy%2C%20is%20an%20umbrella%20syndicate%20arranging%20online%20platforms%20for%20enabling%20illegal%20betting%20websites%20to%20enrol%20new%20users%2C%20create%20user%20IDs%20and%20laundering%20of%20money%20through%20a%20layered%20web%20of%20benami%20bank%20accounts%2C%20the%20probe%20agency%20has%20alleged.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20new%20rules%20for%20online%20gaming%2C%20the%20government%20has%20prohibited%20any%20game%20that%20involves%20betting%20and%20wagering.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%20a%20dozen%20other%20celebrities%20and%20actors%20are%20under%20the%20agency%20scanner%20in%20this%20case%20and%20they%20will%20also%20be%20summoned%20soon%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20probe%20agency%2C%20which%20investigates%20financial%20fraud%2C%20seized%20assets%20worth%20Rs%20417%20crore%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20online%20betting%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20promoters%2C%20who%20hail%20from%20Bhilai%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20were%20running%204-5%20such%20apps%2C%20all%20of%20them%20earning%20a%20profit%20of%20around%20Rs%20200%20crore%20per%20day%2C%20said%20the%20probe%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20gaming%20app%20is%20run%20from%20a%20central%20head%20office%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20the%20probe%20agency%20investigation%20has%20shown.%20The%20app%20also%20has%20its%20call%20centres%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELarge%20expenditure%20in%20cash%20is%20also%20being%20done%20in%20India%20for%20advertising%20of%20betting%20websites%20to%20attract%20new%20users%20and%20franchise%20(panel)%20seekers%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696416900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Fv7p1kmvo_-ranbir-kapoor_625x300_10_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franbir-kapoor-summoned-by-enforcement-directorate-over-case-involving-gaming-app-4449006%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actor%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20on%20Friday%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20case%20involving%20a%20gaming%20app.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franbir-kapoor-summoned-by-enforcement-directorate-over-case-involving-gaming-app-4449006%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franbir-kapoor-summoned-by-enforcement-directorate-over-case-involving-gaming-app-4449006%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franbir-kapoor-summoned-by-enforcement-directorate-over-case-involving-gaming-app-4449006%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Caste%20Count%20A%20Turning%20Point%20In%20Indian%20Politics%2C%20Just%20Before%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20government's%20caste%20survey%20report%2C%20released%20on%20October%202%2C%20has%20opened%20the%20floodgates%20for%20caste%20reconfigurations%20and%20realignments%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20survey%2C%20timed%20just%20six%20months%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20will%20have%20wider%20ramifications%20for%20political%20parties%20at%20the%20national%20and%20state%20levels.%20There%20is%20a%20clamour%20for%20similar%20exercises%20in%20other%20states%2C%20with%20regional%20parties%20believing%20it%20will%20only%20benefit%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20recent%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20had%20already%20called%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20the%20country.%20With%20this%20masterstroke%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Lalu%20Yadav%20-%20the%20veterans%20of%20caste%20engineering%20-%20have%20set%20the%20agenda%20for%20political%20parties.%20The%20country%20may%20witness%20a%20second%20Mandal-Mandir%20political%20match%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20next%20year's%20national%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20caste-based%20survey%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Bihar%20Jaati%20Adharit%20Ganana%2C%20was%20launched%20by%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar-led%20government%20in%20January.%20Its%20aim%20was%20to%20improve%20the%20lot%20of%20backward%20communities%20and%20ensure%20better%20implementation%20of%20welfare%20schemes.%20In%20the%20caste%20and%20community-based%20vote%20bank%20politics%20of%20Bihar%2C%20an%20overall%20statistics%20of%20the%20state's%20caste%20demographics%20would%20certainly%20influence%20the%20ruling%20coalition's%20strategies%20and%20policies%2C%20particularly%20linked%20to%20social%20justice%20and%20welfare.%20In%20fact%2C%20there%20are%20no%20surprises%20in%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20caste%20break-up%20shows%20that%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%20(EBCs)%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20form%2084%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20electorate.%20Upper%20castes%2C%20with%20a%2010.5%20per%20cent%20share%20in%20the%20population%2C%20will%20have%20no%20major%20impact%20on%20the%20math.%20The%20Muslim%20(17.7%20per%20cent)%20-Yadav%20(14.26%20per%20cent)%20combination%20will%20call%20the%20shots%2C%20with%2032%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuslims%20have%20been%20voting%20as%20one%20homogenous%20bloc%20for%20INDIA%20parties%20until%20now.%20The%20EBC%20population%20of%2036%20per%20cent%20(including%20more%20than%20100%20castes%2C%20including%20Nitish%20Kumar's)%20has%20always%20oscillated%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20opposition.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20caste%20survey%20is%20bound%20to%20trigger%20spinoffs%20in%20other%20states.%20The%20demands%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20are%20focused%20on%20proving%20that%20the%20OBC%20population%20far%20exceeds%20the%2027%20per%20cent%20reservation%20limit%20and%20that%20urgent%20correction%20is%20due.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20call%20for%20enhancing%20the%20quota%20beyond%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20cap%20suggested%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20new%20opposition%20formula%20%26quot%3BPDA%26quot%3B%20-%20pichhde%20(Backward)%2C%20Dalit%2C%20alpasankhyak%20(Minority)%20-%20is%20central%20to%20its%20strategy%20for%202024.%20Mayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20and%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA's%20alliance%20partners%2C%20the%20Nishad%20Party%20and%20OP%20Rajbhar's%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20(SBSP)%2C%20are%20all%20for%20a%20caste%20census.%20The%20Congress%20has%20promised%20a%20survey%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Jharkhand%20assemblies%20have%20already%20endorsed%20the%20demand%20for%20caste%20surveys.%20Down%20South%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%20have%20completed%20similar%20surveys%20and%20but%20have%20not%20revealed%20the%20data.%20Only%20Bengal's%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20opposed%20the%20census.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20emerging%20scenario%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20long%20before%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20revises%20her%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20realised%20the%20importance%20of%20bringing%20its%20OBC%20leaders%20to%20prominence%20(Siddaramaiah%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20in%20Rajasthan).%20However%2C%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20do%20that%20in%20the%20northern%20Hindi%20belt%20states%20like%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20demonstrated%20to%20its%20rivals%20how%20Mandal%20and%20Kamandal%20could%20be%20a%20formula%20for%20electoral%20success.%20The%20party%20has%20also%20projected%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20the%20face%20of%20the%20OBC%20in%20national%20politics%20(DON'T%20THINK%20IT%20IS%20SUBTLE).%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20the%20BJP%20continues%20to%20find%20the%20task%20of%20balancing%20its%20traditional%20upper%20caste%20support%20base%20and%20its%20recent%20success%20in%20reeling%20in%20OBCs%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20these%20balancing%20challenges%20of%20the%20BJP%20that%20its%20political%20opponents%20sense%20an%20opportunity%20to%20weaken%20the%20ruling%20party's%20social%20and%20ideological%20appeal%20amongst%20the%20OBCs%2C%20STs%20and%20SCs.%20Thus%2C%20an%20increasing%20demand%20for%20caste-based%20enumeration.%20What%20is%20unsaid%20is%20the%20BJP's%20huge%20dilemma%20in%20all%20this.%20If%20it%20supports%20a%20caste%20count%2C%20it%20could%20alienate%20its%20traditional%20upper-caste%20supporters.%20If%20not%2C%20it%20could%20end%20up%20angering%20its%20OBC%2C%20ST%20and%20SC%20supporters.%20In%20either%20scenario%2C%20its%20Hindutva%20appeal%20to%20voters%20is%20weakened.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20may%20confront%20fresh%20challenges%20internally%20in%20maintaining%20the%20organisational%20and%20power%20balance%3B%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20possibility%20of%20a%20churning%20within%20the%20OBC%20bloc.%20Until%20recently%2C%20a%20larger%20percentage%20of%20relatively%20well-off%20OBCs%20like%20the%20Yadavs%2C%20Kurmis%20and%20Jats%2C%20had%20benefitted%20from%20the%20caste-centric%20census.%20This%20can%20serve%20to%20heighten%20political%20consciousness%20amongst%20numerically%20smaller%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20many%20smaller%20OBC%20caste-centric%20parties%20have%20emerged%20on%20the%20electoral%20horizon%2C%20in%20states%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Rajasthan.%20A%20caste%20count%20can%20generate%20new%20political%20forces%20never%20really%20anticipated%20by%20established%20OBC%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EComing%20soon%2C%20perhaps%20-%20the%20BJP's%20counter%20strategy%20to%20consolidate%20Hindus%20under%20its%20flag%20amid%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20caste-focused%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696416900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F346936jg_bihar-caste-survey-ndtv-650_650x400_02_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcaste-count-a-turning-point-in-indian-politics-just-before-2024-4449152%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bihar%20government's%20caste%20survey%20report%2C%20released%20on%20October%202%2C%20has%20opened%20the%20floodgates%20for%20caste%20reconfigurations%20and%20realignments%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcaste-count-a-turning-point-in-indian-politics-just-before-2024-4449152%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcaste-count-a-turning-point-in-indian-politics-just-before-2024-4449152%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcaste-count-a-turning-point-in-indian-politics-just-before-2024-4449152%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3BLittle%20Surprise%20For%20Ma%26quot%3B%20From%20His%20Goa%20Trip%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20introduced%20the%20world%20to%20the%20newest%20member%20of%20his%20family%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20a%20pet%20dog%20named%20Noorie.%20It%20is%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20little%20surprise%20for%20his%20mother%2C%20ex-Congress%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Gandhi%20went%20to%20Goa%2C%20in%20August%2C%20to%20bring%20Noorie%2C%20a%20Jack%20Russell%20Terrier%20puppy%2C%20home.%20Noorie%20was%20adopted%20from%20a%20dog%20kennel%20in%20North%20Goa's%20Mapusa.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20occasion%20of%20World%20Animal%20Day%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20shared%20a%20heartwarming%20video%20on%20YouTube.%20The%20clip%20opens%20with%20Mr%20Gandhi%20talking%20about%20his%20surprise%20plan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CA%20little%20surprise%20for%20Ma%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul%20as%20he%20requests%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20to%20step%20out%20of%20the%20house.%20A%20few%20seconds%20later%2C%20the%20veteran%20politician%20is%20seen%20making%20her%20way%20to%20the%20table%20and%20removing%20the%20cover%20of%20the%20box.%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20looks%20super%20happy%20after%20meeting%20Noorie%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20so%20cute.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAlong%20with%20the%20video%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20you%20all%20to%20meet%20the%20newest%20and%20the%20cutest%20member%20of%20our%20family%20-%20our%20li'l%20pup%2C%20Noorie.%20She%20flew%20in%20from%20Goa%20straight%20into%20our%20arms%20and%20has%20become%20the%20light%20of%20our%20lives.%20Unconditional%20love%20and%20uncompromising%20loyalty%20-%20there%20is%20so%20much%20this%20beautiful%20animal%20can%20teach%20us!%20We%20must%20pledge%20to%20prot