er_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-surprises-mother-sonia-gandhi-with-pet-dog-noorie-4449070%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20introduced%20the%20world%20to%20the%20newest%20member%20of%20his%20family%20a%20pet%20dog%20named%20Noorie.%20It%20is%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20little%20surprise%20for%20his%20mother%2C%20ex-Congress%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-surprises-mother-sonia-gandhi-with-pet-dog-noorie-4449070%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-surprises-mother-sonia-gandhi-with-pet-dog-noorie-4449070%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-surprises-mother-sonia-gandhi-with-pet-dog-noorie-4449070%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Delivers%20On%20Caste%20Count.%20Over%20To%20INDIA%20Parties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20Gandhi%20Jayanti%2C%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20in%20Bihar%20released%20the%20findings%20of%20its%20statewide%20caste%20survey%2C%20intensifying%20the%20battle%20for%20the%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Class)%20vote%20and%20setting%20the%20opposition%20agenda%20for%202024.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20also%20called%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20the%20caste%20report.%20He%20has%20been%20batting%20for%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bjiski%20jitni%20sankhya%20bhaari%20uski%20utni%20hissedaari%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20have%20been%20pitching%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20at%20the%20national%20level%20for%20scientific%20and%20targeted%20welfare%20of%20OBCs.%20It%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20revive%20Mandal%202.0%20as%20a%20counter%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Kamandal%202.0%2C%20that%20is%20the%20grand%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20January.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20deserves%20credit%20for%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20the%20caste%20count%20was%20carried%20out%20and%20the%20report%20released%20-%20something%20even%20Manmohan%20Singh%20in%202011%20and%20Siddaramaiah%20during%20his%20previous%202013-18%20tenure%20could%20not%20achieve%2C%20despite%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20shows%20that%20a%20whopping%2084%25%20of%20the%20population%20in%20Bihar%20belongs%20to%20the%20OBC%20(Backward%20Caste%2B%20Extremely%20Backward%20Class)%2C%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20category.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20praised%20the%20findings%20as%20historic%20and%20reiterated%20that%20only%20three%20out%20of%2090%20secretaries%20in%20the%20Indian%20government%20belonged%20to%20OBCs.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20termed%20it%20a%20tool%20of%20divisive%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%20thrown%20up%20by%20the%20caste%20survey%20are%20in%20line%20with%20the%20earlier%20estimates%2C%20more%20or%20less%20-%20the%20minority%20population%20of%2017%25-18%25%20largely%20seem%20to%20have%20classified%20themselves%20as%20Backward%20Caste%20or%20Extremely%20Backward%20Class%20(12%25)%20and%20the%20balance%205%25%2C%20under%20the%20general%20category.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20eyes%20will%20be%20on%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20next%20move.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20have%20earlier%20supported%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20higher%20reservation%20of%2050%25%20for%20OBCs%20and%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20cap%20on%20reservations.%20They%20hope%20to%20galvanize%20the%20OBC%20voters%20through%20this%20demand%20and%20make%20a%20serious%20dent%20in%20the%20BJP%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20is%20trying%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20champion%20of%20OBCs%2C%20a%20position%20which%20Modi%20enjoys%20currently%2C%20and%20corner%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20BJP%20receives%20the%20highest%20OBC%20support%20(44%25)%2C%20riding%20on%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20OBC%20identity%20and%20creating%20a%20wedge%20between%20dominant%20and%20non-dominant%20EBCs.%20INDIA%20boasts%20of%20parties%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20that%20are%20dominated%20by%20Yadav%20and%20Jat%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lower%20OBCs%20have%20not%20benefited%20from%20current%20quotas%3B%2025%25%20sub-caste%20are%20occupying%2097%25%20of%20government%20jobs%20and%20admissions%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%20report%20in%20the%20media.%20The%20BJP%20has%20used%20this%20well%20to%20create%20a%20trust%20deficit%20between%20lower%20and%20upper%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20could%20drive%20home%20the%20narrative%20that%20if%20EBCs%20have%20not%20benefited%20in%20the%20current%20reservation%20system%2C%20how%20can%20they%20get%20justice%20in%20a%20larger%20reservation%20pool.%20If%20the%20narrative%20of%20the%20opposition%20gains%20momentum%2C%20then%20the%20BJP%20could%20even%20implement%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%20in%20the%20Winter%20session%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20propose%20a%20quota%20within%20quota%20for%20lower%20or%20extremely%20backward%20OBCs%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20higher%20than%20the%20sub-limit%20for%20upper%20OBCs%20like%20Yadavs%2C%20Kurmis%20etc%2C%20as%20they%20have%20been%20the%20largest%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20current%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20could%20permanently%20alienate%20upper%20OBCs%20like%20Yadavs%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20could%20consolidate%20the%20party's%20hold%20over%20EBCs.%20The%20BJP%20got%2065%25%20EBC%20vote%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%202022%20and%2045%25%20in%20Karnataka%20per%20Axis-My%20India%20exit%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20be%20a%20backup%20plan%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20checkmate%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Mandal%202.0%20project%2C%20the%20party's%20ultimate%20aim%20being%20to%20divide%20Hindu%20votes%20through%20this%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20double-edged%20sword%20for%20the%20opposition.%20Ostensibly%2C%20the%20demand%20is%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20OBCs%2C%20but%20this%20will%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20demand%20for%20OBC%20reservation%2C%20which%20could%20put%20off%20middle%20and%20rich%20socio-economic%20class%2035%25-36%25%20voters%20and%20general%20category%20voters%20(12%25-15%25)%20at%20the%20national%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20also%20be%20turned%20around%20by%20the%20BJP.%20It%20can%20say%20the%20Congress%20is%20demanding%20reservation%20for%20minorities%20(not%20allowed%20by%20Constitution)%20which%20could%20increase%20confrontation%20and%20result%20in%20polarisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20through%20their%20labharthi%20schemes%2C%20has%20given%20a%20class%20tadka%20to%20caste%20politics.%20This%20has%20fostered%20identity%20issues%20-%20the%20voter%20is%20OBC%20first%20or%20poor%2Fmiddle%20class%20later%2C%20and%20vice%20versa.%20Politics%20has%20moved%20beyond%20caste%20politics%2C%20even%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%20Development%2C%20beneficiary%20status%2C%20and%20leadership%20have%20become%20very%20important.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnly%204%25%20of%20the%20people%20cited%20caste%20as%20a%20reason%20for%20voting%20for%20a%20particular%20party%20in%20UP%20in%202022.%20It%20has%20been%20somewhat%20able%20to%20break%20caste%20barriers%2C%20besides%20the%20trump%20card%20of%20Hindutva%20and%20nationalism%2C%20to%20unite%20OBCs%20under%20its%20umbrella.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBackward%20Castes%20and%20EBCs%20are%20not%20a%20homogenous%20vote%20bloc%2C%20and%20even%20in%20Bihar%2C%20may%20not%20have%20the%20impact%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20hopes%20for.%20It%20could%20open%20up%20a%20Pandora's%20Box.%20This%20could%20increase%20demand%20for%20an%20EBC%20chief%20minister%20and%2For%20a%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20-%20both%20positions%20are%20currently%20occupied%20by%20upper%20OBCs.%20INDIA%20was%20being%20shown%20ahead%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20by%20surveys%2C%20even%20as%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20switched%20sides%20before%20the%20caste%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYadavs%20hold%20seven%20of%20the%2031%20minister%20spots%20in%20Bihar%2C%20which%20is%2022.6%25%20and%201.5%20times%20their%20population%20strength.%20Similarly%2C%20four%20ministers%2C%20including%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20belong%20to%20the%20Kurmi-Koeris.%20This%20is%20double%20their%20proportion%20of%20the%20population.%20It%20is%20often%20said%20that%20charity%20begins%20at%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20and%20INDIA%20have%20thrown%20the%20caste%20census%20dart%20in%20the%202024%20game%20hoping%20this%20will%20power%20their%20campaign%20and%20enable%20them%20to%20make%20a%20dent%20in%20the%20BJP's%20OBC%20support%2C%20without%20which%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20beat%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696416780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F94mspj98_nitish-kumar-pti-_625x300_03_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnitish-kumar-delivers-on-caste-count-over-to-india-parties-4445253%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20INDIA%20have%20thrown%20the%20caste%20census%20dart%20in%20the%202024%20game%20hoping%20this%20will%20power%20their%20campaign%20and%20enable%20them%20to%20make%20a%20dent%20in%20the%20BJP's%20OBC%20support%2C%20without%20which%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20beat%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canon