riety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Fmonica-lozano-julio-rojas-nicolas-acuna-1235744348%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Fmonica-lozano-julio-rojas-nicolas-acuna-1235744348%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Modi%20Govt%20May%20Say%20Mother%20of%20Democracy%2C%20But%20Is%20Turning%20India%20Into%20a%20Graveyard%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04135208%2Fsignal-2023-10-03-165845.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Professor%20Gyan%20Prakash%2C%20historian%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhistory.princeton.edu%2Fpeople%2Fgyan-prakash%5C%22%3EDayton-Stockton%20Professor%20of%20History%20at%20Princeton%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20a%20rich%20body%20of%20work%20on%20modern%20South%20Asian%20history%2C%20colonialism%2C%20post-colonial%20theory%2C%20urban%20history%2C%20global%20history%20and%20history%20of%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%202018%20book%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FEmergency-Chronicles-Indira-Democracys-Turning%2Fdp%2F0670088242%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Emergency%20Chronicles%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20Democracy%E2%80%99s%20Turning%20Point%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20very%20well-regarded%20scholarly%20work%20on%20the%20national%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20in%201975%2C%20when%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20then%20a%20student%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20was%20kidnapped%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police%20and%20went%20on%20to%20serve%20a%20long%20jail%20sentence.%20Prakash%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F986421%2Femergency-chronicles-how-newsclicks-prabir-purakayastha-was-abducted-by-the-police-as-a-student%5C%22%3Etracks%20his%20example%20as%20a%20metaphor%20for%20the%20abuse%20of%20power.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20being%20apprehended%20in%202023%20under%20charges%20of%20terrorism%20under%20the%20draconian%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20is%20a%20different%20kettle%20of%20fish%2C%20Prakash%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%201974%2C%20what%20India%20saw%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20lawful%20suspension%20of%20the%20law%E2%80%9D.%20This%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20completely%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20disagrees%20with%20people%20comparing%20this%20to%20what%20happened%20in%201975.%20%E2%80%9CIndira%20Gandhi%20had%20the%20Youth%20Congress.%20They%20were%20nothing.%E2%80%9D%20This%2C%20he%20says%2C%20reeks%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctotalitarianism%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20desire%20to%20remake%20India%20in%20a%20different%20mould.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20things%20are%20at%20work%20here%2C%20according%20to%20Prakash.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20a%20threat-perception%20that%20the%20Modi-led%20government%20senses%20that%20despite%20the%20popular%20vote%20in%20two%20consecutive%20elections%2C%20that%20something%20is%20remiss%20and%20the%20control%20%E2%80%9Cis%20not%20complete%E2%80%9D.%20The%20result%20then%2C%20%E2%80%9Cis%20to%20control%20every%20person%20who%20thinks.%E2%80%9D%20If%20you%20show%20signs%20of%20%E2%80%9Cthinking%2C%20being%20able%20to%20change%20your%20mind%E2%80%9D%20having%20ideas%20and%20a%20vision%20different%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20and%20leaders%2C%20you%20will%20be%20throttled%20and%20proscribed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20aspect%20which%20is%20more%20serious%20and%20also%20different%20from%20the%20Emergency%20is%20%E2%80%9Cto%20achieve%20total%20domination%20of%20the%20person%20by%20killing%20the%20juridical%20person%20in%20a%20human%20being%20or%20in%20a%20citizen.%20And%20you%20do%20that%20by%20creating%20a%20system%20of%20law%2C%20outside%20the%20normal%20penal%20system.%20So%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20file%20an%20FIR%20through%20the%20normal%20procedural%20system.%20You%20charge%20him%20through%20the%20UAPA%2C%20which%20creates%20a%20completely%20different%20circle%20around%20this%20person.%20I%20am%20not%20being%20hyperbolic%20but%20this%20is%20comparable%20to%20the%20way%20in%20which%20the%20concentration%20camp%20functions.%20The%20concentration%20camp%20was%20outside%20the%20normal%20penal%20system.%20People%20who%20went%20there%2C%20had%20no%20right!%20They%20were%20outside%20any%20kind%20of%20juridical%20system%2C%20any%20protection%20of%20law%20and%20so%2C%20you%20know%2C%20you%20create%20a%20criminal%2C%20you%20create%20a%20terrorist%20by%20completely%20killing%20all%20the%20juridical%20protection%20a%20citizen%20has%2C%20or%20a%20human%20being%20has%20in%20a%20system%20of%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20Prakash%20fears%20for%20Purkayastha%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20so%20sorry%20he%20is%20having%20to%20go%20through%20this%20again.%E2%80%9D%20But%20he%20fears%20much%20more%20for%20India%20and%20what%20the%20abandonment%20of%20democratic%20norms%20means%20for%20India.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20about%20citing%20democratic%20values%20and%20holding%20them%20to%20account.%E2%80%9D%20Regimes%20like%20this%20have%20a%20different%20way%20of%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrakash%20referred%20to%20a%20seminar%20on%20democracy%20he%20attended%20with%20colleagues%20last%20week%20where%20scholars%20from%20Poland%20and%20Hungary%20(in%20deep%20democratic%20backslide%2C%20like%20India)%20shared%20experiences%20of%20how%20the%20belief%20was%20in%20one%20leader%20and%20whatever%20he%20said%20was%20the%20truth.%20Prakash%20pointed%20out%20to%20ex-US%20President%2C%20Donald%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20supporters%20too%2C%20suspending%20judgement%20as%20they%20believed%20in%20their%20%E2%80%9Cone%20leader.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20will%20it%20all%20end%3F%20Answering%20that%2C%20Prakash%20said%20what%20is%20most%20important%20is%20what%20happens%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20day%20after%E2%80%9D.%20On%20the%20day%20when%20such%20regimes%20are%20defeated%20%E2%80%9Cand%20I%20hope%20they%20will%20be%2C%20when%20India%20trumps%20the%20BJP%20in%202024.%E2%80%9D%20But%20the%20next%20day%2C%20the%20laws%20and%20the%20tools%20of%20authoritarianism%20they%20leave%20behind%2C%20are%20hard%20to%20deactivate.%20Also%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20poison%20they%20have%20spread%20in%20society%E2%80%9D%20would%20need%20to%20be%20dealt%20with%2C%20that%20is%20a%20very%20major%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FPe6uCBXHWYg%3Fsi%3DQyvke7_JY45TUsE_%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22896%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696408259000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04135208%2Fsignal-2023-10-03-165845.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgyan-prakash-modi-govt-prabir-purkayastha%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20wrong%20to%20compare%20this%20repression%20to%20the%20Emergency%20in%201975%2C%20historian%20Gyan%20Prakash%20said.%20This%20is%20accompanied%20by%20spreading%20poison%20and%20society%20and%20an%20attempt%20to%20remake%20India%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20a%20cult.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgyan-prakash-modi-govt-prabir-purkayastha%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nupur%20on%20clashing%20with%20sister%20Kriti%20at%20the%20BO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696408143000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104154964%2Cimgsize-73888.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnupur-sanons-reacts-to-ganapath-and-tiger-nagesw