te%2C%20and%20Congress%20intended%20to%20deter%20religious%20persecution%20and%20promote%20freedom%20of%20religion%20and%20belief.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20on%20September%2020%20discussed%20%E2%80%9Cenforced%20discriminatory%20policies%20targeting%20religious%20minorities%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3Eviolence%20in%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Nuh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20targeted%20attacks%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcatholic-church-leaders-in-kerala-condemn-modi-govt-for-alleged-genocide-in-manipur%5C%22%3EChristians%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Findias-bnei-menashe-community-in-crisis-as-manipur-rocked-by-ethnic-violence%2F%5C%22%3EJewish%3C%2Fa%3E%20minorities%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20participants%20of%20the%20hearing%20offered%20policy%20options%20for%20the%20United%20States%20to%20work%20with%20India%20to%20combat%20abuses%20of%20religious%20freedom%20and%20related%20human%20rights%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CReligious%20freedom%20conditions%20in%20India%20have%20notably%20declined%20in%20recent%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20USCIRF%20chair%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscirf.gov%2Fabraham-cooper%5C%22%3EAbraham%20Cooper%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CMuslims%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdata-rise-in-attacks-on-christians-in-india-up-four-times-in-11-years-2012-2022%5C%22%3EChristians%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20Adivasis%20are%20experiencing%20increased%20levels%20of%20attacks%20and%20acts%20of%20intimidation.%20Authorities%20have%20continued%20to%20suppress%20minority%20voices%20and%20those%20advocating%20on%20their%20behalf.%20These%20trends%2C%20and%20their%20implication%20for%20US%20foreign%20policy%2C%20should%20not%20be%20ignored.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20body%20also%