muan%20Vaiphei%20from%20Kuki-dominated%20Churachandpur%2C%20who%20was%20beaten%20to%20death%20by%20a%20mob%20on%20May%203%20while%20in%20police%20custody%2C%20has%20heard%20nothing%20about%20how%20her%20son%E2%80%99s%20case%20is%20progressing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20has%20contacted%20us%20to%20record%20out%20statement%2C%20and%20the%20police%20has%20given%20us%20no%20relief%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20Vaiphei%E2%80%99s%20body%20is%20still%20in%20a%20mortuary%20in%20Imphal%2C%20as%20the%20family%20is%20unable%20to%20make%20the%20journey%20to%20claim%20it%20due%20to%20the%20existing%20social%20divisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20case%20highlighted%20by%20the%20newspaper%2C%20Imphal-based%20Kavita%20Singh%20does%20not%20know%20if%20her%20government%20employee%20husband%20is%20dead%20or%20alive.%20He%20and%20another%20Meitei%20man%20were%20last%20seen%20near%20Kangpokpi%20district%20on%20May%206%2C%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20news%20of%20them%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20case%20of%20my%20missing%20husband%20and%20his%20friend%20to%20CBI%2C%20but%20we%20have%20no%20update%20on%20whether%20that%20has%20happened.%20Police%20have%20not%20reached%20our%20home%2C%20or%20updated%20us%20on%20any%20progress%20in%20investigations.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20relief%20from%20the%20government%2C%20and%20my%20husband%E2%80%99s%20salary%20has%20also%20not%20been%20paid%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20serious%20concern%20during%20the%20violence%20has%20been%20the%20looting%20of%20state%20armouries.%20In%20total%2C%20nearly%204%2C500%20weapons%20and%20around%20650%2C000%20rounds%20of%20ammunition%20have%20gone%20missing.%20Of%20these%2C%20only%201%2C500%20arms%20and%20around%2015%2C000%20pieces%20of%20ammunition%20have%20been%20recovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeep%20divisions%20have%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbuffer%20zones%E2%80%9D%20between%20Meitei-dominated%20and%20Kuki-dominated%20areas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20are%20not%20able%20to%20access%20these%20zones.%20Between%20Churachandpur%20and%20Imphal%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmanipur-police-kept-out-of-buffer-zones-550232%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20are%20four%20barricades%20%E2%80%93%20manned%20by%20the%20Army%2C%20the%20second%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20the%20third%20by%20the%20BSF%20and%20the%20last%20one%20by%20the%20CRPF%20(all%20central%20forces).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20media%20these%20locations%20with%20heavy%20presence%20of%20Central%20forces%20are%20known%20as%20buffer%20zones.%20We%20call%20them%20hotspots.%20The%20multiple%20barriers%20set%20up%20before%20Churachandpur%20is%20one%20of%20those%20hotspots.%20There%20are%20a%20number%20of%20such%20hotspots%20across%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kuldiep%20Singh%2C%20a%20former%20CRPF%20DG%20who%20has%20been%20appointed%20Security%20Adviser%20to%20the%20state%20government%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20buffer%20zones%2C%20combines%20with%20widespread%20internal%20migration%2C%20have%20also%20reportedly%20complicated%20the%20Manipur%20Police%E2%80%99s%20investigations%20and%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696393299000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22095913%2FF6ga_ibawAAlDWp.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ffive-months-into-manipur-conflict-justice-evades-those-who-lost-their-loved-ones%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20government's%20statistics%2C%20178%20people%20have%20been%20killed.%20Civil%20society%20groups%20put%20this%20number%20at%20close%20to%20200.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20have%20been%20displaced.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUr