%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695994869000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331317%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20English%20teacher%20forced%20to%20beg%20on%20Chennai's%20streets%20to%20survive%2C%20Merlin%20Paati%20from%20Myanmar%20found%20shelter%20and%20a%20dignified%20livelihood%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20viral%20video%20shot%20by%20content%20creator%20Mohamed%20Ashik.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331317%2Fheartwarming-why-a-81-yo-homeless-woman-got-500k-followers-in-4-days%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20Survived%20an%20Acid%20Attack%20at%2014%2C%20Today%20I%20Rescue%20Victims%20%26amp%3B%20Provide%20Free%20Legal%20Aid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mentions%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20and%20domestic%20violence%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDevanshi%20Yadav%20(31)%20was%20just%20nine%20months%20old%20when%20she%20lost%20her%20father.%20When%20Devanshi%20was%2014%2C%20she%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328258%2Fdevanshi-yadav-bareilly-ngo-legal-help-sexual-abuse-victims-domestic-violence%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattacked%20with%20acid%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20a%20boy%20after%20she%20rejected%20his%20advances.%20The%20left%20side%20of%20her%20body%20was%20burnt.%20It%20took%20a%20long%20time%20for%20her%20to%20heal%20physically%2C%20but%20what%20hurt%20more%20was%20the%20victim%20shaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20pain%20was%20unbearable%2C%20it%20was%20the%20comments%20from%20people%20that%20left%20me%20shaken.%20People%20would%20shame%20me%20and%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20the%20way%20you%20dress%3B%20you%20asked%20for%20it!%E2%80%99%20After%20a%20year%2C%20the%20scars%20started%20to%20fade%2C%20but%20the%20incident%20wrecked%20my%20self-confidence%20and%20left%20me%20very%20scared%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20activist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20was%20recovering%2C%20a%20family%20friend%20tried%20to%20assault%20her.%20When%20he%20did%20it%20again%2C%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330948%2Fp-bindu-organic-farmer-tamil-nadu-innovation-msme-kvk-agriculture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebroke%20her%20silence.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Realising%20that%20there%20were%20many%20like%20her%20who%20must%20be%20afraid%20to%20speak%20up%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20to%20help%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETaking%20strength%20from%20her%20father%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20stories%20I%20remember%20are%20of%20him%20being%20a%20great%20human%20being%20and%20a%20servant%20of%20the%20society.%20Even%20from%20a%20young%20age%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20like%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20she%20started%20an%20NGO%20in%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20honour%20called%20Shaheed%20Ramashray%20Welfare%20Society%20in%20Bareilly%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20helping%20victims%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20and%20domestic%20violence%20get%20justice.%20The%20welfare%20society%20gives%20them%20free%20legal%20aid.%20Devanshi%20also%20gives%20them%20free%20counselling%20and%20accompanies%20victims%20to%20the%20police%20station%20and%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGetting%20proper%20counselling%20and%20knowing%20the%20next%20steps%20is%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20healing%20after%20abuse.%20The%20people%20who%20come%20to%20me%20are%20usually%20very%20scared%20and%20unsure%20of%20what%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327829%2Flilyma-khan-head-chef-at-dear-donna-delhi-shares-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einjustices%20and%20horrible%20things%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20suffered%20should%20not%20be%20the%20fate%20of%20anyone%20else.%20Life%20really%20knocked%20me%20down%20and%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20help%20people%20who%20were%20suffering.%20To%20me%2C%20this%20fight%20is%20personal%20and%20I%20will%20take%20it%20as%20far%20as%20I%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWatch%20this%20video%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20Devanshi%E2%80%99s%20journey%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCxqVDAwB22S%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCxqVDAwB22S%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCxqVDAwB22S%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2F