years%20later%2C%20his%20father%20bought%20him%20some%20engineering%20books%2C%20which%20sealed%20his%20love%20for%20the%20subject.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20four%20engineering%20books%20that%20my%20father%20bought%20at%20Rs%202%20in%201961-62%20opened%20up%20a%20whole%20new%20world%20to%20me.%20Those%20books%20are%20my%20Bible%2C%20and%20I%20still%20have%20them%20and%20the%20Meccano%20set%20with%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2079-year-old.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20model%20making%20and%20engineering%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20pursue%20mechanical%20engineering%20in%20Pune.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20art%20of%20design%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20718px)%20100vw%2C%20718px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-26-at-15.48.01-1695822992.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22718%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ISRO%20rocket%20models%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-26-at-15.48.01-1695822992.jpeg%20718w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-26-at-15.48.01-1695822992-135x300.jpeg%20135w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-26-at-15.48.01-1695822992-460x1024.jpeg%20460w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-26-at-15.48.01-1695822992-689x1536.jpeg%20689w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-26-at-15.48.01-1695822992-150x334.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331081%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EISRO%20rocket%20models%20made%20by%20Craftizan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%