though%20their%20art%20is%20greatly%20admired%2C%20the%20village%20artisans%20have%20struggled%20with%20poverty%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESwarnalata%20Nayak%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20this%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317479%2Fart-historian-anitha-n-works-with-siddi-women-to-sell-kavandi-quilts-karnataka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20artisan%20community%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20spent%20her%20early%20married%20life%20looking%20after%20her%20in-laws%20and%20children.%20Wanting%20to%20send%20her%20children%20to%20a%20good%20school%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20join%20her%20husband%20in%20the%20craft%20work.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20money%20coming%20into%20the%20house%20was%20not%20enough%20to%20send%20my%20children%20to%20a%20good%20school.%20However%2C%20even%20after%20the%20two%20of%20us%20started%20working%20together%2C%20we%20were%20still%20not%20able%20to%20afford%20the%20fees%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20toil%20and%20dedication%20of%20these%20artisans%20are%20often%20met%20with%20meagre%20wages.%20Swarnalata%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20wages%20can%20plummet%20as%20low%20as%20Rs%201%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20which%20is%20hardly%20enough%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%E2%80%9D%20Balancing%20household%20chores%20and%20contributing%20to%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20craftwork%20had%20become%20increasingly%20taxing%20for%20Swarnalata.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20something%20changed.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20friend%20who%20introduced%20me%20to%20the%20Karya%20Project%20and%20suggested%20I%20get%20involved.%20The%20work%20is%20quite%20simple%3B%20all%20I%20have%20to%20do%20is%20speak%20in%20Odiya%20on%20my%20phone%2C%20it%20gets%20recorded%2C%20and%20then%20I%20get%20paid!%E2%80%9D%20Swarnalata%20informs%20that%20she%20was%20paid%20Rs%204%2C000%20after%20working%20for%20just%20one%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEstablished%20